transform.tRule:
# Special support for Irish initial n (eclipsis/urú)
# https://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/Appendix:Irish_mutations#Effects_of_eclipsis
# and t-prothesis
# https://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/Appendix:Irish_mutations#T-prothesis
$bow = [\ $];
::NFD();
$bow } n { [AEIOU] → n \-;
$bow } t { [AEIOU] → t \-;
::NFC();
::Any-Lower();
